{"questionId":"25387","questionHtml":"<p>For triangular numbers, verify that&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mfenced><mi>n</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mfenced><mi>n</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfenced><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></mfenced><mi>n</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; OR&nbsp; <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mfenced><mi>n</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mfenced><mi>n</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A0A1</strong></em> if&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mfenced><mi>n</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;only is seen.</p>\n<p>Do not award any marks for numerical verification.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>so for triangular numbers,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mfenced><mi>n</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mn>2</mn></